<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>
<HR>
</P>
<P>KB_Lyria wrote:</P>
<P>Please make it so that casting a song automatically stops the old song and starts the new one.</P>
<P>
<HR>
</P></BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
<DIV>I dont agree with this.&nbsp; I wouldnt like to have my songs starting on their own.&nbsp; Part of the reason my mez isnt on a (/stopsong, /cast #) hotkey is so I can turn off songs with a single press.&nbsp; It'd be nice if clicking the item casting your song stoped it, but I really dont see how this effects a twist horribly.&nbsp; Tap gem 1, double tap gem 2, double tap gem 3, tap gem 3, tap gem 4, double tap gem 1.&nbsp; Of course Im quite dense, but I just dont see it, but I support anything that helps save Bardic wrists.</DIV>
