												<DIV>Oh, one other thing to think about.&nbsp; We're the only class that has to macro or double tap to cast spells.&nbsp; You got want to lay down 3 nukes with your wizard?&nbsp; Press 1, 2, then 3.&nbsp;&nbsp; You want to debuff, slow, and dot with your shaman?&nbsp; Press 1, 2, then 3.&nbsp; You want to keep 3 songs up with your bard?&nbsp; I press 1, 2, then 3 cause I have /stopsong /cast # macroed, but if you don't do it my way, you'll be pressing 1,1,2,2,3,3 and that's why you get carpal twice as fast =).&nbsp; Since your role is to chain cast for hours on end, anything that saves keystrokes is just putting off your doctor's visit by that much longer =).</DIV>
																		
